      "content": "It makes sense to feel that way; the universe doesn't care about our struggles, and that realization can be incredibly freeing from the pressure of meaning. If nothing lasts, then the only logic that matters is the one you find in your own heart, not some grand cosmic design. You can stop fighting the void and instead lean into the quiet, honest truth of your existence right now.",
